HEADWORD: Tusk
<hw>Tusk</hw> <pr>(t⟦ucr⟧sk)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>Same as <er>Torsk</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
